00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,740
Press the highlighted button to pull up the game menu.

2
00:00:03,580 --> 00:00:07,240
If you forget the controls at any point, you can come back here to find them again.

3
00:00:08,500 --> 00:00:12,940
From this screen, you can adjust the volume, turn on subtitles, and turn on live controller

4
00:00:12,940 --> 00:00:16,080
diagrams to show you which buttons you are pushing as you push them.

5
00:00:16,720 --> 00:00:20,480
If you feel disoriented floating in space, you have the option to turn on a floor.

6
00:00:21,280 --> 00:00:24,840
The current objective can always be found in this menu if you get stuck.

7
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:29,680
It is best to go through the game in order, but you have the option to select different

8
00:00:29,680 --> 00:00:30,800
scenes from this menu.

9
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:33,540
You can replay the tutorial at any point.

10
00:00:34,160 --> 00:00:35,580
Select scene 1 to begin.

